      "page_number": 1,
      "raw_text": "The Washington Water Power\nCo. has begun work on the prelim-\nmary arrangements for it's big\npower dam to be erected at Little\nFalls on the Spokane river.\nGround has been bought at Rear\ndan, on which bunk houses for the\nworkmen, stables for the horses\nand storage buildings for mate\nrails will be erected. A private\nline of railway will connect Rear\ndan with Little Falls, a distance\nof Is miles. The new dam will\ncost 81 900 900."
